{"tid":2437733,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"挑戰 Gmail 電郵服務   華為「花瓣郵箱」開放註冊","createTime":"2021-03-08T05:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T01:39:47.000Z","uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"80ce5aa980092ce3651dbe37f60b3cd1021c4e5d","tid":2437733,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:10:46.000Z","msg":"受到美國商務部實體清單的影響，Google 無法向華為提供他們的程式和服務，華為於是在過去兩年加緊開發自家 Huawei Mobile Service（HMS）和一系列對應的服務，例如 HMS Core、AppGallery 程式商店、Petal Search 和 Petal Maps。<br />\n<br />\n至於 Google 其中一項最多人註冊使用的 Gmail 電郵服務，華為亦在最近開始提供自家版本。消息指華為最近開放 Petal Mail（花瓣郵箱）的試用，讓中國用戶可以註冊，成功註冊會獲得 @petalmail.com 電郵地址。現階段 Petal Mail 還在初步測試階段，所提供的亦是相當基礎的電郵服務。<br />\n<br />\n跟 Gmail 的界面設計和功能類似，除了收件箱、草稿箱、寄件箱等基本功能，亦提供垃圾郵件、加星和歸檔的進階功能。暫時未知 Petal Mail 會在何時全面推出，亦未知會否如 AppGallery 等在中國以外的海外市場提供服務。<br />\n <br />\n資料來源：gizchina<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/217874/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4546%2F217874%2F1%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058jYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=e7245512\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4546/217874/1/</a>"},{"pid":"dfa5747ae55bbcf4151ac66e5b86e601e8aa48c4","tid":2437733,"uid":9193,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:12:13.000Z","msg":"email自動送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85683a28a9feec537537e60c3615b172fb20dcc","tid":2437733,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dfa5747ae55bbcf4151ac66e5b86e601e8aa48c4","tid":2437733,"uid":9193,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:12:13.000Z","msg":"email自動送中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm